{"tid":1233491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係唔比你衝，衝都請等有人支援先！！","createTime":"2019-06-16T19:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T20:24:33.000Z","uid":203845,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"194f4cb61169cae90f77c7d0a75a5b8de2941284","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:06:14.000Z","msg":"我知大家都好想衝，大家都好激動，但係都請大家睇一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實而家林奠係絕對可以挽回劣勢，只要大家一衝動，佢就可以有返民意<br />\n<br />\n第一，撤走警犬。當然唔係真係撤走，而係喺「適當」嘅時候出手。佢地會一直暗中睇<br />\n<br />\n第二，派人搞示威者。今次佢唔單止要搞亂，更加真係要派人打示威者，從而製造寒蟬效應。係，警犬唔可以打示威者，唔可以打記者。咁其他市民（黑社會or公安）呢？佢地出手打邊個都可以。理所當然地，警犬比人撤走，自然就可以咩都睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n第三，當演變成流血，先派警犬清場。到時候警犬就會變成出師有命<br />\n<br />\n咁做有咩好處？<br />\n<br />\n第一：市民注意力會轉移，變成反暴力行為，而唔再係反政府，咁自然林奠就冇人理會<br />\n<br />\n第二：幫警犬挽回形象。而家佢地係出師有命，邊個敢話佢地？<br />\n<br />\n第三：幫建制派挽回選票。當香港亂嘅時候，中立嘅人就會由而家支持泛民變做寧願維穩，然後建制派又可以用遣責暴力事件，重申吸納選票<br />\n<br />\n最後：因為逃犯條例少咗關注，亦都少咗人企出嚟，通過亦都唔再係難事。大家呢兩個禮拜日，612嘅抗爭都會白費<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力。唔係話衝嘅人係鬼，只係喺呢個形勢下，大家應該更加深思熟慮，要衝嘅，最好等日頭多人支援，又多記者影住嘅情況下先衝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ea5728a8df796e73137c1cab5c35a38b516ebf","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:06:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82b1a4637d45141998e042d1e2b86d9a026925e","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:07:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d14ece66a4f43191545794e0c915f2114d050d2","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:08:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家小心呀"},{"pid":"2256786b745eab88b2151637ad4e8bc628c6e2d6","tid":1233491,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:08:40.000Z","msg":"開水馬築防線 有心就坐6點班車出黎"},{"pid":"d65855a76498abd2478b5ea8fe832028dbf2bd33","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2256786b745eab88b2151637ad4e8bc628c6e2d6","tid":1233491,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:08:40.000Z","msg":"開水馬築防線 有心就坐6點班車出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:09:16.000Z","msg":"聽日一定會嚟，但係今晚請留力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c342b8d5241e1b936389a0324fe101648a58648","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:09:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6da6f1534b918d0dc7a8e6d8bcd02f889bdd8f4","tid":1233491,"uid":236140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2256786b745eab88b2151637ad4e8bc628c6e2d6","tid":1233491,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:08:40.000Z","msg":"開水馬築防線 有心就坐6點班車出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:10:07.000Z","msg":"未到六點就清左你啦 <br />\n<br />\n太少人啦"},{"pid":"58c1a48e03c3d06951fe31081d7d68f231fbf714","tid":1233491,"uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"都冇人話要而家衝 我見佢地守啫"},{"pid":"dde6b0bb4f930768958fbcd6b4f2a96a0dcd5619","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:11:02.000Z","msg":"我相信而家嘅人唔係鬼，大家亦應該要團結。但係而家真係唔係衝嘅好時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7694132d2bc2a63604a8b763cf63e6b287cab88e","tid":1233491,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:11:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"427bed31b4098a8c7a81cc57dffb936d788b958e","tid":1233491,"uid":52271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:11:41.000Z","msg":"休息好先啦<br />\n班犬瞓足一日涼足一日冷氣<br />\n我地大部分人出黎曬左行左成日<br />\n體力已經輸<br />\n而家大部分人回緊血，你而家衝，冇支援<br />\n同衝出去獻頭冇分別"},{"pid":"0c142f4a3d841f85c4dd9f737a335ee48eb7fd3a","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58c1a48e03c3d06951fe31081d7d68f231fbf714","tid":1233491,"uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"都冇人話要而家衝 我見佢地守啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:11:52.000Z","msg":"但係唔好搞地盤，政府會有籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91005ef1ecc81698e296bdcfb721be1f7996c73d","tid":1233491,"uid":112282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:11:57.000Z","msg":"無人衝啊依家<br />\n唔好再放風話有人想衝"},{"pid":"f5e772172e0fd06844c56eaff68f10f229ad527b","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91005ef1ecc81698e296bdcfb721be1f7996c73d","tid":1233491,"uid":112282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:11:57.000Z","msg":"無人衝啊依家<br />\n唔好再放風話有人想衝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:12:23.000Z","msg":"咁就好，大家留力聽日"},{"pid":"6c03d00f845d7c8258f461a32e5d9883847a107f","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:13:52.000Z","msg":"而家我地民意真係贏緊。贏係因為團結<br />\n所以<br />\n第一：唔好捉鬼<br />\n第二：大家留力，要多人，多記者嘅時候先做嘢"},{"pid":"332787179f6b0113df0751031c15d083fc5735c8","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:15:15.000Z","msg":"各位義士，真係留力聽日，大家返去瞓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a460fa5a3c368152ec9348d341d3b1112ec9448","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:17:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445003e3b946eb2d3558e0542cb3355a7f6b23a9","tid":1233491,"uid":260139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:18:22.000Z","msg":"<em>呢場仗係有排打<br />\n時機未到呀巴打</em>"},{"pid":"23842b7e9be51ff6de1cc7903dcfe6ae15d98f7c","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"445003e3b946eb2d3558e0542cb3355a7f6b23a9","tid":1233491,"uid":260139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:18:22.000Z","msg":"<em>呢場仗係有排打<br />\n時機未到呀巴打</em>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:19:10.000Z","msg":"呢場係持久戰，大家走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日先係重點呀"},{"pid":"29e4951f8d09563328ee5297fbf9a53d2fbe4bb2","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:19:54.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以認真睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8c994c5ebd45c2c933c93de7fbca59ccd04972","tid":1233491,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:21:33.000Z","msg":"基本原則：<br />\n日頭先去「示威」，夜晚就和理非<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個人意見：<br />\n1.）<span style=\"color: gold;\">敵不動，我不動</span><br />\n政府暫緩可能係十日八日，但亦都有可能係十個月八個月，參考2014雨革，佔領冇乜可能維持到咁耐，不如大家先休息一下，等他朝政府真係想再推出，泛見議員一定會事先被通知，佢哋會再發動群眾運動，到時再出手都未遲<br />\n（呢個亦都可以視為解決成個問題嘅方法）<br />\n<br />\n2.）都係嗰句，「<span style=\"color: gold;\">一個冇人冇會開嘅立法會你衝嚟有乜意義姐？</span>」雖然呢句係由一哥講出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我覺得係有道理，值得花時間諗下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係唔想再有義士要白白犧牲，大家呢排受過太多肉體同精神上嘅傷害啦，我希望大家可以休息返陣，當前局勢下我希望「留得青山在」係最好嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3641e7fe47c6dae07c5a8c5e4d5108a3e99241b","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a8c994c5ebd45c2c933c93de7fbca59ccd04972","tid":1233491,"uid":226955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:21:33.000Z","msg":"基本原則：<br />\n日頭先去「示威」，夜晚就和理非<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個人意見：<br />\n1.）<span style=\"color: gold;\">敵不動，我不動</span><br />\n政府暫緩可能係十日八日，但亦都有可能係十個月八個月，參考2014雨革，佔領冇乜可能維持到咁耐，不如大家先休息一下，等他朝政府真係想再推出，泛見議員一定會事先被通知，佢哋會再發動群眾運動，到時再出手都未遲<br />\n（呢個亦都可以視為解決成個問題嘅方法）<br />\n<br />\n2.）都係嗰句，「<span style=\"color: gold;\">一個冇人冇會開嘅立法會你衝嚟有乜意義姐？</span>」雖然呢句係由一哥講出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我覺得係有道理，值得花時間諗下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係唔想再有義士要白白犧牲，大家呢排受過太多肉體同精神上嘅傷害啦，我希望大家可以休息返陣，當前局勢下我希望「留得青山在」係最好嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:22:08.000Z","msg":"啱呀，唔好再犧牲<br />\n一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5730eab424909a37640f1445b49091b79407c869","tid":1233491,"uid":40350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"well said<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d8f88a49076582ab406fa717ef063dfb47e2ed","tid":1233491,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:23:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}